                </p>

                <h4 class="h4 card__heading">Revocation of your consent to the processing of data</h4>

                <p class="card__text">
                    A wide range of data processing transactions are possible only subject to your express consent. You can also
                    revoke at any time any consent you have already given us. To do so, all you are required to do is to send us an
                    informal notification via e-mail. This shall be without prejudice to the lawfulness of any data collection that
